<div
  style="
    max-width: 600px;
    min-width: 300px;
    margin: 40px auto;
    box-shadow: 0px 0px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    font-size: 16px;
    padding: 20px;
    background-color: #4c83ff;
    border-radius: 3px;
    color: #fff;
  "
>
  <h3 style="margin-bottom: 40px">Hi! 亲爱的用户:</h3>
  <p>您正在进行邮箱验证, 本次请求的验证码为:</p>
  <p>
    <strong style="color: #ea5455; font-size: 24px">
      <%= locals.code %>
    </strong>
    <span>(为了保障您帐号的安全性, 请在 30 分钟内完成验证)</span>
  </p>
  <p>
    <span>快速访问: </span>
    <a
      href="https://iceweather.netlify.app/"
      style="color: #fff"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >https://iceweather.netlify.app/</a
    >
  </p>
  <p style="margin-top: 40px; text-align: right"><%= locals.sign %></p>
  <p style="text-align: right"><%= locals.date %></p>
</div>
